-down-millions-to-return-to-former-studio-for-next-movie-3803833">拒绝了重返华纳兄弟拍摄下一部电影的机会，</a>尽管华纳兄弟向他提供了七位数的支票。这位导演从 2002 年的<em>《失眠》</em>一直在这家电影公司工作，直到 2020 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/tenet"><em>《信条》</em></a>上映。 </p><figure id="attachment_3821774" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3821774" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3821774" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Christopher-Nolan-Photo-by-Vivien-Killilea_Getty-Images-for-Paramount-Pictures.jpg" alt="克里斯托弗·诺兰" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Christopher-Nolan-Photo-by-Vivien-Killilea_Getty-Images-for-Paramount-Pictures.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Christopher-Nolan-Photo-by-Vivien-Killilea_Getty-Images-for-Paramount-Pictures-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Christopher-Nolan-Photo-by-Vivien-Killilea_Getty-Images-for-Paramount-Pictures-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Christopher-Nolan-Photo-by-Vivien-Killilea_Getty-Images-for-Paramount-Pictures-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Christopher-Nolan-Photo-by-Vivien-Killilea_Getty-Images-for-Paramount-Pictures-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Christopher-Nolan-Photo-by-Vivien-Killilea_Getty-Images-for-Paramount-Pictures-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3821774" class="wp-caption-text">克里斯托弗·诺兰 – 图片来源：Vivien Killilea/派拉蒙影业的盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/christopher-nolan-hits-out-at-warner-bros-for-putting-2021-slate-on-hbo-max-its-very-very-messy-2833999">他批评华纳兄弟计划在</a>电影院和流媒体服务<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/hbo-max">HBO Max</a>上同时发行 2021 年电影后，他决定转投环球影业。诺兰还免除了某些费用，以确保<em>《信条》</em>在影院上映。</p><p> <em>《奥本海默》</em>成为诺兰<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/oppenheimer-reaches-new-box-office-milestone-internationally-3615370">海外票房最高的影片</a>，该片在全球获得超过 9.6 亿美元（7.57 亿英镑）的票房收入。这部电影仍然是诺兰全球第三大卖座电影，仅次于<i>《黑暗骑士》</i>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-dark-knight-rises"><i>《黑暗骑士崛起》</i></a> ——这两部电影的票房收入均超过十亿。</p><p> <i>《NME》</i>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/oppenheimer-review-christopher-nolan-3470392">对该片的五星级评论</a>中表示：“<i>奥本海默</i>不仅是对原子弹背后的人的权威描述，也是成人电影制作领域的一项里程碑式的成就。多年来，诺兰一直在完善严肃大片的艺术——制作巧妙、精心调整、引人注目的多厅史诗片；除了在电影院之外，无法不间断、不受干扰地观看这些内容。但不知何故，这感觉更大。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/christopher-nolans-next-film-will-be-an-adaptation-of-homers-the-odyssey-3824603">克里斯托弗·诺兰的下一部电影将改编自荷马的《奥德赛》，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 《浴血黑帮》的创作者史蒂文·奈特暗示了电影后期计划并预告了新剧集https://www.nme.com/news/tv/peaky-blinders-creator-steven-knight-hints-at-post-movie-plans-and-teases-new-series-3824585?utm _source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=peaky-blinders-creator-steven-knight-hints-at-post-movie-plans-and-teases-new-seriesAneesa Ahmed Mon, 23 Dec 2024 22:02:58 +0000 Film NewsNewsTV NewsTV https://www.nme.com/?p=3824585 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Peaky-Blinders-creator-Steven-Knight.-Credit-Jacob-King.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="《浴血黑帮》的创始人史蒂文·奈特。信用 - 雅各布·金" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Peaky-Blinders-creator-Steven-Knight.-Credit-Jacob-King.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Peaky-Blinders-creator-Steven-Knight.-Credit-Jacob-King-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Peaky-Blinders-creator-Steven-Knight.-Credit-Jacob-King-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Peaky-Blinders-creator-Steven-Knight.-Credit-Jacob-King-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Peaky-Blinders-creator-Steven-Knight.-Credit-Jacob-King-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Peaky-Blinders-creator-Steven-Knight.-Credit-Jacob-King-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>随着希里安·墨菲主演的电影拍摄结束，奈特暗示了“新一代”节目的想法</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/peaky-blinders-creator-steven-knight-hints-at-post-movie-plans-and-teases-new-series-3824585">《浴血黑帮》的后创作者史蒂文·奈特暗示了电影后的计划，并预告了</a>首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上出现的新剧集。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Peaky-Blinders-creator-Steven-Knight.-Credit-Jacob-King.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="《浴血黑帮》的创始人史蒂文·奈特。信用 - 雅各布·金" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Peaky-Blinders-creator-Steven-Knight.-Credit-Jacob-King.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Peaky-Blinders-creator-Steven-Knight.-Credit-Jacob-King-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Peaky-Blinders-creator-Steven-Knight.-Credit-Jacob-King-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Peaky-Blinders-creator-Steven-Knight.-Credit-Jacob-King-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Peaky-Blinders-creator-Steven-Knight.-Credit-Jacob-King-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Peaky-Blinders-creator-Steven-Knight.-Credit-Jacob-King-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>随着希里安·墨菲主演的电影拍摄结束， <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/peaky-blinders"><em>《浴血黑帮</em></a>》的主创史蒂文·奈特暗示将推出“新一代”剧集。</p><p>该剧第六季于 2022 年上映，但奈特希望用一部故事片来结束墨菲饰演的汤米·谢尔比和其他犯罪伙伴的故事，而不是第七季。</p><p><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/peaky-blinders-movie-cast-plot-release-date-tommy-shelby-3814955">这是我们所知道的关于电影《浴血黑帮》的一切</a></strong></p><p>这部电影由奈特编剧，汤姆·哈珀执导，汤姆·哈珀执导了该剧的三集。墨菲将再次扮演谢尔比，配角包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stephen-graham">斯蒂芬·格雷厄姆</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rebecca-ferguson">丽贝卡·弗格森</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/barry-keoghan">巴里·基奥根</a>和蒂姆·罗斯。该片将由<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix</a>发行，但上映日期尚未确定。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.parismatch.com/people/info-match-le-createur-de-peaky-blinders-steven-knight-devoile-son-nouveau-projet-244756" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《巴黎竞赛》</em></a>的最新采访中， <em>《浴血黑帮》</em>的电影已经拍摄完毕，奈特谈到了该片的未来。他还暗示可能会推出新一代角色的后续作品。</p><p> “我们将在一个发生在第二次世界大战后的系列剧中关注新一代。然后，谁知道呢？为什么不推出服装系列呢？”他说道（由<a href="https://screenrant.com/peaky-blinders-movie-filming-wrap-release-window-new-show-plan-steven-knight/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>ScreenRant</em></a>翻译）。</p><p>除了奈特在采访中的评论之外，发型和化妆设计师纳迪亚·史黛西 (Nadia Stacey) 最近还发布了有关电影即将结束的消息，并以“不朽的男人 - 浴血黑帮电影”作为标题开头，暗示了即将推出的项目的可能标题。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DDjVYjMK4JS/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06 563.154,70.057 562.10